                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850223-92-off430 t17850223-92-cd431"></join> last, and feloniously stealing therein five silk handkerchiefs, value 15 s. and twelve silk and cotton handkerchiefs, value 25 s.
            </rs> the property of the said 
               <persName id="t17850223-92-person951">
                  John
                   Hawkins
               <interp inst="t17850223-92-person951" type="surname" value="Hawkins"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850223-92-person951" type="given" value="John"></interp>
